      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «سَيْرُ اَلْمَنَازِلِ يُنْفِدُ اَلزَّادَ وَ يُسِيءُ اَلْأَخْلاَقَ وَ يُخْلِقُ اَلثِّيَابَ وَ اَلسَّيْرُ ثَمَانِيَةَ عَشَرَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2516 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Frequent travel depletes provisions, worsens manners, and wears out clothing. Travel is [ideally] for eighteen days.\""
        ]
      }
    },
